title._content: Picknick bij Aalsmeer / Having a picnic near the Dutch bulb fields

description._content: Nationaal Archief / Collectie SPAARNESTAD PHOTO/Cevirum, SFA002008530 Gezin aan het picknicken bij de bollenvelden van Aalsmeer, Nederland, 1960. . Dutch family having a picnic near the bulbfields of Aalsmeer, the Netherlands, 1960.
